| style="color:#000; padding:2px 5px;" | <div id="mp-itn"><div style="float:right;margin-left:0.5em;">
[[File:Neil Robertson at Snooker German Masters (DerHexer) 2013-02-02 01 cropped.jpg|link=File:Neil Robertson at Snooker German Masters (DerHexer) 2013-02-02 01.jpg|100x100px||Neil Robertson at the Snooker German Masters in 2013|alt=Neil Robertson at the Snooker German Masters in 2013]]</div>
* In [[horse racing]], [[California Chrome]] ridden by [[Victor Espinoza]] wins the '''[[2014 Kentucky Derby|Kentucky Derby]].'''
* The Ukrainian government '''[[Siege of Sloviansk#Second_offensive|launches an offensive]]''' on [[2014 pro-Russian unrest in Ukraine|pro-Russian rebels]] in [[Sloviansk]] while '''[[2 May 2014 Odessa clashes|clashes in Odessa]]''' kill more than 40 people.
* '''[[2014 Badakhshan mudslides|Two mudslides]]''' in [[Badakhshan]], Afghanistan, kill at least 350 people and displace 4,000 others.
* More than 50 royal mummies are discovered in Egypt's '''[[KV40]]''' tomb.
* '''[[Neil Robertson (snooker player)|Neil Robertson]]''' ''(pictured)'' becomes the first [[snooker]] player to make 100 [[century break]]s in a single season.
* [[2014 Ürümqi attack|'''A bomb blast''']] in [[Ürümqi]] kills 3 people and injures 79 others.
